{"tid":1925792,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(iOS) Assoluto Racing","createTime":"2020-03-14T15:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T11:43:49.000Z","uid":295729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c36369640f4d04165e1438936bc83dfd339b82b0","tid":1925792,"uid":295729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:43:51.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲有玩呢隻racing game？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ykip9cm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkip9cm.png&h=b97b4875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個感覺好Gran Turismo<br />\n車種多，舊到新嘅都有 (有license)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VnjppLN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVnjppLN.png&h=cd4099cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9foYucs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9foYucs.png&h=8dd177a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6rVW0i8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6rVW0i8.png&h=ed47b04f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n時間賽，考牌，比賽<br />\n有賽道，山路(Touge)，RALLY<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3OSVwrr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3OSVwrr.png&h=9a32e5f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yqXVwrs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyqXVwrs.png&h=491b8d96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋<strong>Nurburgring</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a6QHbsA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa6QHbsA.png&h=ac33e78c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫面都算靚，行60fps<br />\n仲可以改performance，外觀，Camber offset<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSet胎壓, 較gear ratios, 換slick tire<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nexqTGi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnexqTGi.png&h=a4fb8677&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AtwjdGJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAtwjdGJ.png&h=b6d30e75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最重要係可以連機一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人有興趣玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以開8人房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b14874ae33168d7a261ff76cf0b64a03442829d","tid":1925792,"uid":48039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:46:26.000Z","msg":"An機有冇"},{"pid":"6677fd6196043f787146c149e846cf6ab9f09645","tid":1925792,"uid":295729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b14874ae33168d7a261ff76cf0b64a03442829d","tid":1925792,"uid":48039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:46:26.000Z","msg":"An機有冇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:53:26.000Z","msg":"應該有，個水印有Android logo"},{"pid":"55d878a73c99e85e96168787ca15d8ff67ef8eb8","tid":1925792,"uid":48039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6677fd6196043f787146c149e846cf6ab9f09645","tid":1925792,"uid":295729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b14874ae33168d7a261ff76cf0b64a03442829d","tid":1925792,"uid":48039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:46:26.000Z","msg":"An機有冇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:53:26.000Z","msg":"應該有，個水印有Android logo"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:59:05.000Z","msg":"隻game原來都差唔多4年前 <br />\n可以down黎望下"},{"pid":"8d7cd0f7638dd039d6345d7ec1d567ac242ef682","tid":1925792,"uid":295729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55d878a73c99e85e96168787ca15d8ff67ef8eb8","tid":1925792,"uid":48039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6677fd6196043f787146c149e846cf6ab9f09645","tid":1925792,"uid":295729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b14874ae33168d7a261ff76cf0b64a03442829